            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> into wedges, then peel and chop the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>into wedges</p><p>After the potatoes have had their initial 15 min, remove the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the oven and move the potatoes to one side</p><p>Add the<strong> tomato wedges </strong>and<strong> onion</strong> <strong>wedges</strong> and return the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> to the oven for a further 15-20 min or until the potatoes have browned and crisped</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
