          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine <strong>half</strong> of the<strong> panko breadcrumbs</strong> with the<strong> grated cheese</strong>, <strong>cooled</strong> <strong>leek</strong>, <strong>egg yolk</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>wholegrain mustard </strong>(save the rest for later!) – this is your <strong>patty mixture</strong></p><p>Season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, then divide the mixture in 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> and shape into patties</p><p>Gently coat the <strong>patties</strong> in the <strong>egg white</strong> and press them into the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>panko</strong> <strong>breadcrumbs </strong>– these are your <strong>Glamorgan-style patties</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
